&lt;div class="hero-eyebrow"&gt;Lightcast US · 29,798 postings · May-Sep 2024&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Salary disparities across&lt;br&gt;disciplines — who benefits&lt;br&gt;most from &lt;span&gt;AI's rise?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class="hero-sub"&gt;
  A data-driven look at how the AI boom is reshaping pay across skills, experience levels, and geographies.
  Six interactive views, drawn from nearly 30,000 US job postings, reveal where the salary story is strongest,
  where the AI premium is real, where it's hype, and where it inverts entirely.
&lt;/p&gt;
